{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Dough","content":["Lightly grease a large bowl. Line baking sheets with parchment paper, lightly sprinkle with semolina and set aside.","Place water, bread flour, semolina, yeast and salt into mixing bowl and knead <b>2 min\/<b>. Form dough into a ball and transfer into prepared bowl. Cover with cling wrap and let dough rise until doubled in size (approx. 1 hr.). Clean mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Filling","content":["Place Parmesan and Fontina cheeses into mixing bowl and grate <b>5 sec\/speed 8<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place sun-dried tomatoes, onions, garlic and basil into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add sausage and pine nuts and cook <b>8 min\/250°F\/\/speed 0.5<b>. Preheat oven to 500°F.","Divide dough into four balls and place two pieces of dough onto each prepared baking sheet. Evenly stretch out each dough into a circle (approx. 6 in.) with lightly floured fingers. Place a fourth of the reserved sausage mixture and grated cheese onto each of the dough rounds, off-centered leaving a ½ inch border. Fold over dough to make a half-circle and pinch to seal.","Brush with egg and sprinkle tops of calzones with dried oregano. Bake for 10-15 minutes (500°F), until golden browned, rotating sheets halfway through baking. Serve warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Dough","content":["olive oil, to grease","semolina, to sprinkle","15 oz warm water (100°F-110°F)","16 oz bread flour","6 oz semolina","2 ¼ tsp rapid rise yeast","1 tbsp salt"]},{"title":"Filling","content":["2 oz Parmesan cheese, cut into 1 in. pieces","2 oz Fontina cheese, cut into 1 in. pieces","4 oz sun-dried tomatoes (in oil), no need to drain","4 oz yellow onions, quartered","1 garlic clove","8 fresh basil leaves (approx. 3 stems)","16 oz Italian sausage, casing removed, cut into 1 in. pieces","1 oz pine nuts","1 large egg, lightly beaten","2 tsp dried oregano              (optional)"]}],"id":"r171201","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-SVfoZHUS4jI\/XZaosa2hRNI\/AAAAAAAAhMo\/mfpsuwZKl6IdFA5BUfsG9jytN-p_PT5ggCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_vGp4-ikR5PNTG_Jg.png","title":"Sausage Calzone with Sun-Dried Tomatoes","publishedAt":"2017-05-12T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"33 g","fat":"38 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"84 g","calories":"3402 kJ \/ 813 kcal"},"usefulItems":"pastry brush, parchment paper, cling wrap, large bowl, baking sheets, oven","basicInfo":["medium","15m","40m","4 pieces"]}